    "body_text": [
        {
            "text": "Undoubtedly the heterologous immune effects of BCG provide a promising avenue for investigation in relation to the COVID-19 pandemic. As cautioned by the WHO, appropriate evidence must be established prior to more widespread use for BCG for this purpose. Three new clinical trials aim to ascertain the protective role of BCG vaccination against COVID-19 virus, a possibility that would have global beneficial implications amidst the current pandemic.",
